WEBVTT

01:07.710 --> 01:10.335
<i>It's like everything
changed in the blink of an eye.</i>

01:10.460 --> 01:12.168
<i>One moment we were fine,</i>

01:12.793 --> 01:15.168
<i>then everything turned to shit.</i>

01:24.835 --> 01:26.793
My little one...

01:27.460 --> 01:30.001
I'm going to miss you all.

01:31.293 --> 01:32.293
Look at me.

01:34.418 --> 01:37.626
We'll write to each other.
You have my address,

01:37.751 --> 01:38.876
don't you?

01:39.918 --> 01:41.918
Then everything's fine.

01:44.960 --> 01:46.001
Off you go.

01:58.210 --> 02:00.626
We'll all miss you, Teacher Dilek.

02:02.585 --> 02:06.085
- Good luck in Istanbul.
- Give your mother my best.

02:07.626 --> 02:08.710
Have a good holiday, Miss.

02:11.918 --> 02:13.251
You're all sad.

02:16.668 --> 02:17.668
Come here.

02:22.043 --> 02:23.210
Selma,

02:23.335 --> 02:25.626
