- No way.

03:48.376 --> 03:49.668
I want another go.

03:50.210 --> 03:51.376
No way!

03:52.460 --> 03:53.918
You cheated.

03:55.043 --> 03:56.501
No, we didn't.

03:59.126 --> 04:00.501
It's not fair.

04:00.626 --> 04:03.043
- You cheated!
- No, we never!

04:03.168 --> 04:04.501
Give her another go.

04:04.626 --> 04:06.251
Everyone gets just one go.

04:06.376 --> 04:08.168
Take your turn!

04:10.418 --> 04:11.543
Let me go!

04:11.918 --> 04:13.085
Let me go!

04:47.835 --> 04:49.251
