05:55.210 --> 05:56.210
Grandma!

05:57.960 --> 05:58.710
Sonay!

05:58.835 --> 06:01.001
Grandma, open the door!

06:01.126 --> 06:02.126
Grandma?

06:03.210 --> 06:04.293
Sonay, are you OK?

06:06.668 --> 06:08.168
Your turn now.

06:08.293 --> 06:09.293
Selma!

06:11.001 --> 06:12.335
Open the door!

06:12.460 --> 06:13.960
Grandma, open up!

06:15.751 --> 06:18.043
Grandma, open the door!

06:25.210 --> 06:27.335
- Get out!
- What's this all about?

06:27.460 --> 06:30.168
- Ece, come here.
- What did we do?

06:32.001 --> 06:33.876
